---
id: "JRN_LinkValidation"
title: Automated Link Validation
description: Verification of internal documentation links during the build process.
trigger: User or Agent runs 'foundryspec build'.
outcome: All links are verified; broken links fail the build.
requirements: REQ_PathIntegrity
---
sequenceDiagram
    participant PER_SystemAnalyst as System Analyst
    participant PER_CodingAgent as Coding Agent
    participant COMP_CLI as FoundrySpec CLI
    participant COMP_Engine as Build Engine
    
    rect rgb(240, 240, 240)
        Note over PER_SystemAnalyst, PER_CodingAgent: Triggered by Manual Build or Agent Maintenance
        PER_SystemAnalyst->>COMP_CLI: runs 'foundryspec build'
        PER_CodingAgent->>COMP_CLI: runs 'foundryspec build'
    end

    COMP_CLI->>COMP_Engine: build()
    COMP_Engine->>COMP_Engine: scanInternalLinks()
    alt Link targets exist
        COMP_Engine-->>COMP_CLI: Verification SUCCESS
        COMP_CLI-->>PER_SystemAnalyst: CLI Output: Success
        COMP_CLI-->>PER_CodingAgent: Exit Code 0 (Success)
    else Broken link found
        COMP_Engine-->>COMP_CLI: Error: Linkage Violation (REQ_PathIntegrity)
        COMP_CLI-->>PER_SystemAnalyst: CLI Output: Error
        COMP_CLI-->>PER_CodingAgent: Exit Code 1 (Fail)
    end
